channel.title: So So Confused
channel.description: Okay uhm anybody whose reading this post :P... How do I add objects to my server I looked through all my files but theres none that have added objects like I want to add a bankbooth to my godwars minigame... but I don't know which folder or file it's in... Someone on my server told me object.cfg But I can't find it help please :confused:

item.title: So So Confused
item.dc:creator: @jackin_jill jackin jill
item.description:
@jackin_jill wrote:

well this might require alot of walking around your server but it works. go into your client.java
search for

public void NewObjects() {
the bank booth id is 2213 you should see a list of things like this
makeGlobalObject(y-cords, x-cords, id, hight, 10);//name of object

look through it and find all the 2213, and go to their coordinate location, then its your decision to move it or to keep it there.

hope this helped ;D
